Identity
public class Staff extends User
The `Staff` class represents staff members in the system who can be associated with various activities and tasks. Staff members are users with specific roles and responsibilities. Staff members inherit properties and methods from the `User` class. They have attributes including an ID, name, email, password, and faculty affiliation. This class is used to create and manage staff members within the system. Staff members can be associated with camps, committees, and other organizational aspects.
